{
  "stem": "268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're already going with a girl, or steady?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we couldn't go to a theater or movie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was more or less our rendezvous, our place to meet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would look forward to-- and this hard work in the factory-- but came weekend, two things to look forward to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At noon in the factory for the meal, they would give us a soup with some potatoes in it and a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then our weekend meeting with other kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those are the two things kept me going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How would you describe the physical look of the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The physical look was at first glance-- and probably second or third glance, too-- sorrowful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was a dilapidated section of town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans would choose a section of town which was run down, houses with leaky roofs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want to categorize our city here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we have sections in this city where-- South Central or places with houses which are in badly need of repair.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's where they would put the Jews in a section like that, houses without even water or sewers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Jewish people who had homes, comfortable homes-- we had a comfortable apartment-- would naturally vacate that and move into one room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And sometimes they would put two-- if there were not enough rooms to go around, they would put two families in it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If there was a single family or a childless family or a family with one child, they would put two of them in the room, which would be a very cramped space.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's how you lived in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And later came the fence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't go across the fence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or even without a fence-- this is the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the boundary.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
